{"type": "article", "id": 26421, "title": "带穗饰的柜子", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-05T07:08:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702142117Jy1BhV8tLzCxaI74.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\"><a href=\"http://www.designattico.com/\">Cristina Celestino</a> 为意大利木制品品牌 <a href=\"http://www.durame.it/\">Durame</a> 设计了这一组名为 Sipario 的柜子。当你掀开穗饰时，就能发现底部其实还藏有一个可以储物的架子。Celestino 的设计灵感来自意大利剧院的构造，覆盖住底座的穗饰就像是幕布一样，拉开后才发现其实别有洞天，造成的反差效果让人对轻与重、光滑与粗糙的差异有了新的思考。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142115omziQM95rBICU1kN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142115jQUdn3vLNJpVxftT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87408313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021421166V725fbAPzyswFaK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021421160OaPdLo1b7nCy5Su.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}